Package: sciscales
Title: Pretty Scientific Notation for ggplot2 Axes
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Christy", "Ray", , "cpickering@jhmi.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7552-9759"))
Description: This package includes functions to convert numbers to customizable 
    scientific format for ggplot axis labels, annotations, and legend labels. It
    works with the labels argument of the ggplot scale functions to integrate 
    easily with existing plots.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
